snippet.title: The Catch: Carp & Coarse | Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Prepare your rod and get ready to cast off as The Catch: Carp & Coarse is out now.

The hunt is on and with 35 species of fish to find, you’ll have to use strategy, skill and tactics to catch the 125 different boss fish found across The Catch: Carp & Coarse’s five venues. Among these are 11 legendary ‘monster’ boss fish - the most elusive, hardest fighting fish in the game.
